data.description: Come see this beautiful home before someone else scoops it up! Remodeled and refreshed inside and out, ready for a quick move-in. Open concept floorplan with huge kitchen and check out that pantry.  Upstairs living would make a great game room, situated more private to the bedrooms. All bedrooms are larger than usual with walk-in closets. The master has two walk-in closets and bonus area that could easily serve as an office, nursery for baby, exercise or cozy sitting area.  You will love the spacious master bath with separate vanities and 2 sinks, jetted tub and separate walk-in shower. Showings by appointment. ALSO FOR LEASE $2300 per mo.
